      "content": "Hey, I need help writing an email to a customer. They bought this really expensive espresso machine from us, but there was a logistics error and now the shipment is two weeks late. I need to apologize and sound professional, but also tell them we'll give them a discount for the trouble. Can you draft something for me?"
